items.title: Titan Company: Robust Q2 growth; healthy long-term prospects
items.description: Titan, a big organised jewellery player, will be the prime beneficiary of the market shift from the unorganised to the organised segment. Moreover, ramping up the non-jewellery business remains an additional growth trigger.

items.title: US antitrust case against Amazon to move forward
items.description: Last year, the FTC alleged Amazon.com, which has 1 billion items in its online superstore, was using an algorithm that pushed up prices U.S. households paid by more than $1 billion. Amazon has said in court papers it stopped using the program in 2019.
